nd without limitations and photo mode allows you to capture and share your creations at the end of each session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109270/extras/gamemodes_gif-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1735022022\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109270/extras/naturalwonders.png?t=1735022022\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nothing can beautify your map more than natural wonders like the snowy Alps, lavender fields or redwood forests, which you can acquire thanks to a unique card upcycle system </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109270/extras/naturalwonders_optimized.gif?t=1735022022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Bitmap Galaxy"],"dlc":[3114870,3114910],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109270/header.jpg?t=1735022022","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Preserve \u00a9 2024. Exclusively Published by Grindstone s.r.o. Developed by Bitmap Galaxy s.r.o. All rights reserved","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Most recent version of Ubuntu LTS<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz Intel<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Intel HD Graphics 5000 (AMD or NVIDIA equivalent)<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> MacOS 11 or later<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3 2.00 GHz or AMD equivalent<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br